genresAdvancedInfo.name: rap toscana
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Rap toscana is a subgenre of Italian rap that originated in Tuscany. It is characterized by its use of the Tuscan dialect and its incorporation of traditional Tuscan music elements. The lyrics often reflect on the region's history, culture, and social issues.
